text: Aimé Verhoeven (born 18 December 1935) is a Belgian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Belgium Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp
